<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥkmẗ ạllh ạlʿly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ḥkmẗ ạllh ạlʿly kyf tqsw ḥạsẖạ klạ
 qlbh ạlṣạlḥ jdạaⁿ ạ̉lạ yḥnw ṣạḥ mhlạ
 ạ̉nt lạ tfhm mạ yjryh ḥqạaⁿ (hw ydry)2
 kl mạ yʿml fhw ạlḥq ṣdqạaⁿ (lst tdry hw ydry)2
 hw ydry dạỷmạaⁿ kl ạlṣlạḥ lnạ jdạaⁿ
 ạ̹n ạ̉fkạrh tʿlw ʿnk ṣạḥ ʿnk jdạaⁿ
 ḥyn yẓlm ạlṭryq lạ trạh (lst wḥdk)2
 yhdy ạ̉qdạmk fy ạlsyr wrạh (dʿh qblk yhdy drbk)2
 ṣạḥb ạlʿrsẖ ydyr ạlkwn ṭrạaⁿ fy ʿnạyẗ
 ạlgẖd ydryʿ bl yjryh ạ̉mrạaⁿ llnhạyh
 kl sẖỷ yʿml llkẖyr ḥtmạaⁿ(hw yjry)2
 flykn fynạ ạlrjạʾ fyh dwmạaⁿ (hw ydry kl ạmr)2
 ḥyn lạ tfhm mạ yjry ṣdyqy tẖq wạ̉mn
 ḥyn lạ tdrk mʿny̱ llṭryq hw ḍạmn
 tẖq bḥb kẖạlṣ blạ ḥdwd (fy ạlmsyḥ)2
 mn fdy̱ ḥtmạaⁿ syʿṭy kl jwd (dẖạ ḥbyby yạ ḥbyby)2</lyrics>
<author>zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, nạṣf ṣbḥy</author>
<hymn_number>6257</hymn_number>
</song>